author: sussman
msg: Fix issue #634:  "URL keyword not expanded"
* props.c (expand_keyword): get the URL value directly from the entry
structure, instead of looking in its 'extra attributes' hash.

author: rooneg
msg: Check the return values from apr-config and apu-config, rather than just
showing a cryptic error when things go wrong.
Patch by: Daniel Berlin <dan@dberlin.org>
* ac-helpers/apr.m4
Test return value of apr-config, rather than assuming it passed.
Issue error messages if it failed.
* aprutil.m4
Ditto.

author: sussman
msg: An interface for Karl and Ben to standardize upon.
* svn_wc.h (svn_wc_merge): public API for doing wc merges via diff3.
Will be used by both 'svn merge' and 'svn update'.
* wc.h (SVN_WC__LOG_MERGE):  declare log wrapper around svn_wc_merge.
